---
title: Tex-Mex Turkey Penne with Crushed Tortilla Chips
description: This delicious, no-fuss pasta dish will satisfy even the pickiest eater! We've packed it with Tex-Mex spices, a cheesy, tangy sour cream sauce and crunchy tortilla chips – and snuck in a few veggies, for good measure.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tex-mex-turkey-penne-eca2d4ae.jpg
